{"tid":336293,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[背叛美帝]菲總統：與中國合作南海探石油","createTime":"2017-07-26T10:24:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-26T11:36:48.000Z","uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"66eabeeb26e00ff69ad9ac17fc015168401fe2e3","tid":336293,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T10:24:04.000Z","msg":"【明報專訊】菲律賓總統杜特爾特24日發表任內第二次國情咨文，其間感謝中國在基建方面提供幫助，他表示：「因為國家發展沒錢，我訪問了中國。他們說，『如果你們沒有資金，我們給你』。我們正在建設新機場，可以從中國那裏借錢。中國承諾給我們免費建兩座大橋。」<br />\n杜特爾特在隨後的記者會上亦透露，菲律賓人民可期待中菲之間的南海聯合石油勘探活動。昨訪菲律賓的中國外長王毅也表示贊同共同開發，稱「共同開發」並不影響也不涉及各自的法律體系，而是通過雙邊協商達成一個彼此都能接受的規範和安排。<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/pns/20170726/s00053/cd8b0e5b90427113c449d3ffe8406f24.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F20170726%2Fs00053%2Fcd8b0e5b90427113c449d3ffe8406f24.jpg&h=09f8d971&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170726/s00013/1501006425137\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170726%2Fs00013%2F1501006425137&d=wUEGWoDItWUnn4dCXV5yAGi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=52e13e1c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170726%2Fs00013%2F1501006425137&h=6ea5fa50\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170726/s00013/1501006425137</a><br />\n作反了"},{"pid":"4f930da701a7162829f3d1169617e5c91159d39c","tid":336293,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T10:44:14.000Z","msg":"有錢乜都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d255fc43672a858588d45f90cdc207ccfa830a7a","tid":336293,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T10:56:15.000Z","msg":"左右逢緣，好撚醒"},{"pid":"5a2277c0e3521499d99efb589ac5b2ce81bda3a4","tid":336293,"uid":38194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score